highlights.text: “Adi Penne” by Stephen Zechariah and Srinisha Jayaseelan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chennai, up 16 spots at #41.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Top Songs Chennai. “Thenmozhi (From "Thiruchitrambalam")” is the highest at #5.
“Thee Thalapathy (From "Varisu")” by Silambarasan TR and Thaman S is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chennai at #14.
“Yaanji - From "Vikram Vedha"” by Sam C.S., Anirudh Ravichander, and Shakthisree Gopalan has been on Top Songs Chennai the longest, at 60 weeks straight.
